For full details of the Wesfarmers' full-year result for 2015, please visit http://t.co/3QoxxV6VSz $WES
. @RGoyder: $WES well placed to strengthen & build upon existing businesses, seeking to deliver improved returns to shareholders
. @RGoyder: Reduced project activity & a focus by major customers on lowering costs were key drivers of the reduced earnings
Earnings at Industrial and Safety division decreased 46.6% to $70m
. @RGoyder: The significant decline in export coal prices adversely affected earnings in the Resources division
Earnings at Resources division down 61.5% to $50m on coal production that was 1.3% lower
. @RGoyder: Kleenheat earnings down due to lower LPG pricing and reduced LPG content in the Dampier to Bunbury natural gas pipeline
. @RGoyder: Good seasonal conditions supported strong earnings growth in fertilisers
. @RGoyder: Chems: Higher earnings in AN & NaCN offset by lower earnings in ammonia and Australian Vinyls
Earnings for WesCEF increased 5.4% to $233m
. @RGoyder: Sales momentum improved through the year as customers responded positively to improvements in Target's range and everyday value
Earnings at Target increased 4.7% to $90m. Revenue decreased 1.8%
. @RGoyder: Customers responded more and more positively to Kmart's compelling offer across its network of stores
Earnings at @Kmart_Australia grew 18.0% to $432m on revenue growth of 8.2%
. @RGoyder: The performance of Officeworks was clearly its best under Wesfarmers' ownership and a highlight for the period
Earnings at @Officeworks increased 14.6% to $118m with revenue growth of 8.8%
. @RGoyder: Bunnings' performance was very strong and reflects sound strategy execution
Earnings at @Bunnings increased 11.1% to $1,088m on revenue growth of 11.6%.
. @RGoyder: @Coles customers responded positively to improvements in product quality, value and availability
. @RGoyder: In a competitive supermarket sector, Coles' improved sales momentum was a good result
EBIT at @Coles increased 6.6% to $1,783m for the FY on revenue growth of 2.2%. Food/liquor sales up 5.3%
. @RGoyder: Cash flow generation was a highlight, supported by working capital improvement and good capital expenditure disciplines
. @RGoyder: Lower commodity prices, reduced activity & customers' cost reduction resulted in challenging environment for industrial bus.
. @RGoyder: Retail businesses grew earnings & benefited from hard work to deliver improved merchandise offer & better value for customers
. @RGoyder: Solid increase in underlying profit for of 2015 is pleasing
